 (1982) J. Sci. Food Agric., 33, pp. 227-230; Wheatley, R.E., Trace gas fluxes from soil-plant systems under present and future climatic conditions (1996) Landbauforsch. Völkenrode Sonderh., 165, pp. 33-41; Yoshida, N., Matsuo, S., Nitrogen isotope ratio of atmospheric N2O as a key to the global cycle of N2O (1983) Geochem. J., 17, pp. 231-239","Anger, M.; Inst. Pflanzenbau Universitat Bonn, Katzenburgweg 5, D-53115 Bonn, Germany; email: m.anger@uni-bonn.de",,,,,,,,09312250,,ZAPFA,,"German","J. Agron. Crop. Sci.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0035210272
